00:07:10.300 --> 00:07:11.710
It just stops blood flow.

00:07:11.710 --> 00:07:19.630
And back in 1990, Dr. Dean Ornish
-- is that a familiar name?

00:07:19.630 --> 00:07:23.980
Dean Ornish won -- he was -- he was
quite a young doctor at the time.

00:07:23.980 --> 00:07:28.780 position:56%
