00:07:53.660 --> 00:07:56.760
OK. Low fat, high in
fiber, no cholesterol.

00:07:56.760 --> 00:07:58.060
That's right.

00:07:58.060 --> 00:08:00.530
OK. Secondly, half
hour walk every day.

00:08:00.530 --> 00:08:03.060
Third, manage stress, which
