00:08:03.060 --> 00:08:04.360
and Washington, D.C.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:05.660
[ Laughing ]

00:08:05.660 --> 00:08:06.960
Avoid tobacco.

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:08.260
And that was the whole program.

00:08:08.260 --> 00:08:10.850
There was no medication
used, no surgery, nothing.

00:08:10.850 --> 00:08:17.310
And he had a comparison group that
