people who don't eat those

00:39:38.290 --> 00:39:39.950
at all are healthier
than the people who do.

00:39:39.950 --> 00:39:41.840
So, we said, "Get rid of them."

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:43.320
And, by the way, people
eat off a plate.

00:39:43.320 --> 00:39:44.690
Give them a plate.

00:39:44.690 --> 00:39:47.520
And we didn't hear back from them.

00:39:47.520 --> 00:39:52.250
Um, so in 2011 we actually
filed suit against the USDA.

00:39:52.250 --> 00:39:54.690
Um, just to compel response.

00:39:54.690 --> 00:39:59.100 position:56%
