00:40:15.810 --> 00:40:17.120
Doesn't have to be meat.

00:40:17.120 --> 00:40:19.250
And there's the dairy
group, but to their credit,

00:40:19.250 --> 00:40:20.900
they said soy milk counts.

00:40:20.900 --> 00:40:22.410
Veganite is good.

00:40:22.410 --> 00:40:24.140
So this is now -- that's My Plate.

00:40:24.140 --> 00:40:25.680
This is now US Government policy.

00:40:25.680 --> 00:40:27.810
So it's not perfect, but
it's definitely going in --

00:40:27.810 --> 00:40:30.560
very much in the right direction.

