the possibilities.

00:41:09.300 --> 00:41:13.300
So whatever you're eating, try
out things that happen to be vegan

00:41:13.300 --> 00:41:14.600
and see if you like them.

00:41:14.600 --> 00:41:17.940
So I take a sheet of paper and I
write, "Breakfast, lunch, dinner,

00:41:17.940 --> 00:41:20.540
snack," on the paper and, for
