and test them out.

00:41:24.640 --> 00:41:27.940
So, I haven't had oatmeal
since I was a kid.

00:41:27.940 --> 00:41:30.030
Maybe with some cinnamon
and some strawberries

00:41:30.030 --> 00:41:32.230
and blueberries maybe
it would taste OK.

00:41:32.230 --> 00:41:34.010
Um, blueberry pancakes?

00:41:34.010 --> 00:41:35.830
I guess I could do that
without the butter.

00:41:35.830 --> 00:41:37.130
That's not so hard.

00:41:37.130 --> 00:41:39.270
Um, I haven't tasted almond milk.

00:41:39.270 --> 00:41:41.200
Hey, have we tasted almond milk?

00:41:41.200 --> 00:41:42.500
Is it good?

00:41:42.500 --> 00:41:43.800
All right.

00:41:43.800 --> 00:41:45.100
OK. Fair enough.

00:41:45.100 --> 00:41:46.400
So you know that.

00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:47.700
You might try oat milk or
hemp milk or something else.

00:41:47.700 --> 00:41:49.000
Just try these different things.

00:41:49.000 --> 00:41:50.300
Same thing for lunch.

00:41:50.300 --> 00:41:51.600
I never had a pizza without cheese.

00:41:51.600 --> 00:41:52.900
How is it?

00:41:52.900 --> 00:41:54.200
I don't know.

00:41:54.200 --> 00:41:55.500
Let's see.

00:41:55.500 --> 00:41:56.800
Um, so all we're doing for week one
is checking out the possibilities.

00:41:56.800 --> 00:42:00.010
We go to an Italian restaurant
and the chef is more than happy

00:42:00.010 --> 00:42:02.930
