00:42:02.930 --> 00:42:06.130
and wild mushrooms and
artichoke hearts and so forth

00:42:06.130 --> 00:42:08.530
and pasta fazol and,
um, healthy things.

00:42:08.530 --> 00:42:13.180
Mexican restaurant, beans and rice,
bean burritos, veggie fajitas, ah,

00:42:13.180 --> 00:42:17.430
Chinese, they got dozens of
things, vegetable dishes,

00:42:17.430 --> 00:42:19.370
rice dishes, tofu dishes.

00:42:19.370 --> 00:42:23.020
Ah, extra points for Japanese
