00:42:36.860 --> 00:42:40.480
and pickles and so forth and
spinach and little red wine vinegar

00:42:40.480 --> 00:42:43.430
and they'll toast it for you
and call it veggie delight.

00:42:43.430 --> 00:42:47.730 position:56%
And Taco Bell is not the pinnacle of
culinary art, but they will be more

00:42:47.730 --> 00:42:49.190
than happy to give
you a bean burrito,

00:42:49.190 --> 00:42:50.490
hold the cheese, and all right.

00:42:50.490 --> 00:42:51.790
So, fair enough.

00:42:51.790 --> 00:42:54.090
So, for the first week, I'm just
checking out the possibilities.

00:42:54.090 --> 00:42:59.670
And then after that do three
weeks all vegan all the time,

00:42:59.670 --> 00:43:04.460
but only 21 days because
you're just testing this diet

00:43:04.460 --> 00:43:06.030
out to see what you think.

00:43:06.030 --> 00:43:09.110
At the end of 21 days two
things will have happened.

00:43:09.110 --> 00:43:12.750
First is you are physically
changing and you will feel it.

00:43:12.750 --> 00:43:14.670
You'll have lost weight
without trying.

00:43:14.670 --> 00:43:16.270
If you have diabetes,

00:43:16.270 --> 00:43:18.700
you'll discover your glucose
numbers are improving.

00:43:18.700 --> 00:43:20.000
Your energy is better.

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:24.060
Your digestion sorts itself out
usually within about 24, 48 hours.

00:43:24.060 --> 00:43:25.800
You just feel dramatically
different.

00:43:25.800 --> 00:43:27.100
Your energy is better.

00:43:27.100 --> 00:43:30.230
Um, anybody watch the Super Bowl,
Tom Brady, as you probably know,

00:43:30.230 --> 00:43:31.860
he threw out the cheese
