00:43:31.860 --> 00:43:33.780
Aaron Rodgers at Green
Bay, same story.

00:43:33.780 --> 00:43:37.150
They're doing this not because they
want to have a healthier figure.

00:43:37.150 --> 00:43:40.410
They're doing this for energy
and to stop inflammation.

00:43:40.410 --> 00:43:42.160
Um, but you -- you
will feel this even

00:43:42.160 --> 00:43:44.210
if you're not a pro
football quarterback.

00:43:44.210 --> 00:43:47.360 position:56%
You discover all those -- my joints.

00:43:47.360 --> 00:43:48.660
I'm better.

00:43:48.660 --> 00:43:49.960
I feel better.

00:43:49.960 --> 00:43:51.890
So that happens in about 21 days.

00:43:51.890 --> 00:43:55.320
Um, the second thing that happens,
though, is your tastes change

00:43:55.320 --> 00:43:56.870
and you didn't expect this.

00:43:56.870 --> 00:43:58.170
But let me ask this group.

00:43:58.170 --> 00:44:00.970
How many of you ever switched
from whole milk to skim milk?

00:44:00.970 --> 00:44:02.570
Let me see hands.

00:44:02.570 --> 00:44:06.580
OK. When you did, what was the
skim milk like at the beginning?

00:44:06.580 --> 00:44:08.930
Watery? Doesn't even look right.

00:44:08.930 --> 00:44:10.390
It's got a blue color.

00:44:10.390 --> 00:44:12.980
How many of you adapted
to it and got used to it?

00:44:12.980 --> 00:44:16.720
OK. Did you ever go back
and taste whole milk again?

00:44:16.720 --> 00:44:19.110
What was that like?

00:44:19.110 --> 00:44:20.410
It's like cream.

00:44:20.410 --> 00:44:21.710
It's -- it's thick.

00:44:21.710 --> 00:44:23.010
Well, wait a minute.

00:44:23.010 --> 00:44:24.310
Your whole life it was fine.

00:44:24.310 --> 00:44:26.660
But when you get a short
break of even a few weeks,

00:44:26.660 --> 00:44:28.110
your taste buds physically adjust.

00:44:28.110 --> 00:44:30.630
They no longer want the fatty
taste, but you will never have

00:44:30.630 --> 00:44:33.740
that experience if you have a
vegan meal on Monday and then one

00:44:33.740 --> 00:44:36.850
on Thursday because in
between you're reawakening

00:44:36.850 --> 00:44:39.170
that fatty desire in
your taste buds.

00:44:39.170 --> 00:44:41.780 position:56%
If, just for a short period like
three weeks, you say, "I'm not going

00:44:41.780 --> 00:44:44.360
to have it," it's like a
smoker not having cigarettes.

00:44:44.360 --> 00:44:46.310
You forget -- you finally
forget about it,

00:44:46.310 --> 00:44:48.480
but you crave today
what you had yesterday.

00:44:48.480 --> 00:44:51.670 position:56%
And you give yourself a 21 day break

00:44:51.670 --> 00:44:53.260
and it gives you power
you didn't have before.

00:44:53.260 --> 00:44:56.040
So that's why we say just do it
for three -- for three weeks.

