00:49:32.450 --> 00:49:33.750
&gt;&gt; Neal Barnard: Sure.

00:49:33.750 --> 00:49:35.050
Um, the question was
what about stress?

00:49:35.050 --> 00:49:36.350
What role does it play?

00:49:36.350 --> 00:49:37.970
Um, I think it plays
a couple of roles.

00:49:37.970 --> 00:49:41.410
One is that when a person is under
either acute or chronic stress,

00:49:41.410 --> 00:49:46.160
the body releases hormones, stress
hormones, cortisol and others.

00:49:46.160 --> 00:49:49.460
And that these do have a
variety of health effects.

00:49:49.460 --> 00:49:50.760
That's number one.

00:49:50.760 --> 00:49:53.430
Number two, when you're
stressed -- is this not true?

00:49:53.430 --> 00:49:56.810
We will eat anything just
to get through that period.

00:49:56.810 --> 00:50:01.620 position:56%
Um, so April 12th, 13th, 14th is not
a time when an accountant is going

00:50:01.620 --> 00:50:03.190
to follow an especially great diet.

00:50:03.190 --> 00:50:06.800
When we're stressed,
we let other things go.

00:50:06.800 --> 00:50:10.140
So stress is -- is an issue and
you should all win the lottery

00:50:10.140 --> 00:50:14.160
and quit your jobs and have
a stress-free existence.

00:50:14.160 --> 00:50:19.290
Um, contrary to that, though,
in World War II pathologists

00:50:19.290 --> 00:50:24.250
who were looking at people who died
of old age, um, were also soldiers

00:50:24.250 --> 00:50:28.260
on the battlefield, what they
found was that those who were

00:50:28.260 --> 00:50:33.010 position:56%
under deprivation, say, like in
Belgium, places where Nazis came in,

00:50:33.010 --> 00:50:38.900
took over, took the meat, took the
cheese, left the local population

00:50:38.900 --> 00:50:43.570
with potatoes and vegetables,
their arteries started to clear

00:50:43.570 --> 00:50:48.800
up even though they were,
arguably, under tremendous stress.

00:50:48.800 --> 00:50:52.730
So I think it is good to contain
stress, but even if you have a lot

00:50:52.730 --> 00:50:55.360
of stress in your life,
when people are

00:50:55.360 --> 00:50:56.820
on a healthful diet,
they seem to do well.

00:50:56.820 --> 00:50:58.470
