00:54:16.110 --> 00:54:17.410
I only -- there's really only two

00:54:17.410 --> 00:54:18.710
that I think people
should really think about.

00:54:18.710 --> 00:54:20.150
Number one is Vitamin B12.

00:54:20.150 --> 00:54:22.910
You need it for healthy
nerves and healthy blood

00:54:22.910 --> 00:54:26.320
and I believe everyone
should take a B12 supplement.

00:54:26.320 --> 00:54:29.870
Second, Vitamin D normally
comes from the sun

00:54:29.870 --> 00:54:33.100
and when we had the good sense
to stay in equatorial Africa,

00:54:33.100 --> 00:54:36.540
we got lots and lots of Vitamin D.
But some of us had the bad judgment

00:54:36.540 --> 00:54:40.020
to move to places like North Dakota
where I grew up, or New Jersey

00:54:40.020 --> 00:54:43.360 position:56%
or Washington, D.C. and even if
there's a lot of sun, we're indoors.

00:54:43.360 --> 00:54:45.590
So a Vitamin D supplement
makes sense.

00:54:45.590 --> 00:54:49.330
How much? About 2,000
international units a day is safe.

00:54:49.330 --> 00:54:52.740
For Vitamin B12, you
need 2.4 micrograms,

00:54:52.740 --> 00:54:54.280
but there's no pill that small.

00:54:54.280 --> 00:54:57.170
So any Vitamin B12 pill you
take has more than enough

00:54:57.170 --> 00:55:00.070
and it's non-toxic even if
you swallow the whole bottle.

00:55:00.070 --> 00:55:02.510
Um, so that's -- that's really it.

